Afro-pop artiste Badman Anchor has dropped the visuals of his debut single 'Badman', off his upcoming album titled Mastermind. This is Anchor's first project and itâ€™s off his debut album set for release later in the year. He has two singles and promises to release more soon. He says he got into music early with encouragement from his mum, who supported him to pursue his dream. Born and raised in Ruiru, Anchor hopes to inspire young upcoming talents in the music industry and also inspire the society through his music. Anchor looks forward to collaborating with local international acts in the next five years to solidify his presence in the industry.